#=GF RA Lu C, Ding F, Chowdhury A, Pradhan V, Tomsic J, Holmes WM, Henkin TM, Ke A
#=GF RL J Mol Biol. 2010;404:803-818.
#=GF RN [9]
#=GF RM 22355167
#=GF RT YbxF and YlxQ are bacterial homologs of L7Ae and bind K-turns but not
